{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodevertical"]}],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","externalID":"c:@E@MLNTextWritingMode@MLNTextWritingModeVertical","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"case","roleHeading":"Enumeration Case","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}]},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeVertical","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"If a text’s language supports vertical writing mode, symbols with point"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"placement would be laid out vertically."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"tokens":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["occ"]}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode"]]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode/MLNTextWritingModeVertical":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical"}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"If a text’s language supports vertical writing mode, symbols with point"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"placement would be laid out vertically."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeVertical","title":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodevertical"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","title":"MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","kind":"symbol","role":"collection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingMode","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The property allows control over a symbol’s orientation. Note that the property"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"values act as a hint, so that a symbol whose language doesn’t support the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided orientation will be laid out in its natural orientation. Example:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"English point symbol will be rendered horizontally even if array value contains"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single ‘vertical’ enum value. The order of elements in an array define priority"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"order for the placement of an orientation variant."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode","title":"MLNTextWritingMode","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode"}}}